text: George Stapf (December 27, 1875 - November 7, 1957) was an American gymnast. He competed in four events at the 1904 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1875 births Category:1957 deaths Category:American male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the United States Category:Gymnasts at the 1904 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from St. Louis
